Package: InterplanetLtx
Type: Package
Title: LTX (Light-Time eXchange) Protocol SDK
Version: 1.0.0
Author: interplanet.live
Maintainer: interplanet.live <hello@interplanet.live>
Description: R implementation of the LTX interplanetary meeting protocol.
    Provides plan creation, segment computation, URL hash encoding/decoding,
    iCalendar generation and delay-matrix utilities for scheduling
    interplanetary communications sessions.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Suggests: base64enc, openssl, jsonlite
